frame Join a battle
participantspacing 15

actor Student
activate Student

Student->System: 1: requestBattlePage()

activate System
System-->Student: 2: show(battle-page)
deactivate System

Student->System: 3: joinBattle(battle)

activate System
alt alreadyJoined == true
System-->Student: show(already-joined Message)
else
System->System: 4: createNewTeam(student)
Student<--System: 5: show(success Message)
end

deactivate System
deactivate Student

